#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_guides/funqy-knative-events.adoc:285
msgid "{quickstarts-tree-url}/funqy-quickstarts/funqy-knative-events-quickstart/src/main/k8s/defaultChain-trigger.yaml[defaultChain-trigger.yaml]"
